OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FJustice at last: Granada Reports' Zoe
OL,7,FMuldoon has this special report on the
OL,8,Fconviction of Paul Quinn.
OL,10,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,11,Fviolently beating and raping a woman
OL,12,Fin 2003 - in an attack that led to the
OL,13,Fwrongful conviction of another man who
OL,14,Fspent 17 years in prison.
OL,16,FPaul Quinn evaded justice for nearly
OL,17,F20 years, but jurors at Manchester
OL,18,FCrown Court found him guilty of rape,
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm, and attempting
OL,20,Fto choke, suffocate or strangle with
OL,21,Fintent. He will be sentenced on 5 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
