PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FThe victim, who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, was walking along
OL,8,FCleggs Lane in Little Hulton, near
OL,9,FSalford, in the early hours of 19 July
OL,10,F2003.
OL,12,FThe then-mother-of-two was pushed down
OL,13,Fan embankment where she was beaten,
OL,14,Fraped and strangled.
OL,16,FDuring the trial, the victim gave
OL,17,Fevidence and told the court her last
OL,18,Fmemory before being strangled
OL,19,Funconscious was a man on top of her
OL,20,Fwith his hands around her neck.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FQuinn always denied any involvement in
OL,7,Fthe brutal attack and was never linked
OL,8,Fto the crime until 2022 when new
OL,9,Fevidence emerged.
OL,11,FThe attack made headlines across the
OL,12,FNorth West, and a clip from a Granada
OL,13,FReports news bulletin was shown to the
OL,14,Fjury in court.
OL,16,FThis clip from Granada Reports was
OL,17,Fshown to the jury in Paul Quinn's trial
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FAn e-fit based on a description of the
OL,7,Fattacker was produced by police, and
OL,8,FAndrew Malkinson was picked out of a
OL,9,Fdigital identity parade by the victim
OL,10,Fand two other witnesses.
OL,12,FNo DNA evidence linked Mr Malkinson to
OL,13,Fthe crime, and he always strenuously
OL,14,Fdenied it, but went on to serve 17
OL,15,Fyears behind bars.
OL,17,FHis conviction was quashed in 2023
OL,18,Fafter his appeal team forced a re-
OL,19,Fexamination of evidence. Mr Malkinson
OL,20,Ffirst appealed against his conviction
OL,21,Fin 2006, but this was dismissed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FHe then made two more attempts, in
OL,7,F2009 and 2018, to ask the Criminal
OL,8,FCases Review Commission to send his
OL,9,Fcase to the Court of Appeal, but both
OL,10,Fwere rejected.
OL,12,FHis final attempt in 2021 led to his
OL,13,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,14,Fallowed by the Court of Appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FQuinn, aged 29 at the time of the
OL,7,Fattack and who lived locally before
OL,8,Fmoving to Exeter, Devon, was only
OL,9,Flinked to the crime in 2012, after
OL,10,Fscientific advances matched his DNA
OL,11,Fprofile from samples left on the
OL,12,Fvictim.
OL,14,FThe DNA findings estimate it would be
OL,15,Fat least one billion times more likely
OL,16,Fif Quinn was a contributor to the
OL,17,Fsample found at the crime scene than
OL,18,Fif he was not.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FFive years before Mr Malkinson's
OL,7,Fconviction was overturned, Paul Quinn
OL,8,Fhad been researching it online.
OL,10,FIn 2019, Quinn visited an article
OL,11,Fabout Mr Malkinson's conviction - then
OL,12,Fmoments later - searched 'wrongful
OL,13,Fconvictions uk'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FIn court, Paul Quinn claimed that his
OL,7,Finternet searches were a 'complete
OL,8,Fcoincidence', but officers from
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Police said at the
OL,10,Ftime of the google search, no-one
OL,11,Fapart from Mr Malkinson and his legal
OL,12,Fteam knew his case was a wrongful
OL,13,Fconviction.
OL,15,FDSI Rebecca McKendrick on some of Paul
OL,16,FQuinn's internet searches
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776600664
OL,3,CMan guilty of rape of woman 23 years
OL,4,Cago in 'miscarriage of justice' case
OL,6,FShortly after news of a DNA
OL,7,Fbreakthrough in the case, Quinn also
OL,8,Fbegan researching how long DNA is kept
OL,9,Fon police databases, whether samples
OL,10,Fcould be removed, and queried "why do
OL,11,FI keep sweating all the time" and "why
OL,12,Fam I sweating so much all of a sudden".
OL,14,FThis was before his arrest on 13
OL,15,FDecember 2022, when Quinn was told for
OL,16,Fthe first time his DNA had been found
OL,17,Fon the victim's clothing,
OL,26,@rD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
